# Users Service

This is the Users Service component of the Flight Reservation System microservices architecture.

## Overview

The Users Service handles user management functionality including user registration, authentication, profile management, and user-related operations within the flight reservation system.

## Features

- User registration and account creation
- User authentication and authorization
- User profile management
- User preferences and settings
- Account verification and password reset

## Architecture

This service is part of a distributed microservices architecture where each service handles specific business domains independently.

## API Endpoints

## Dependencies

- Database for user data persistence
- Authentication service integration
- Message queue for inter-service communication

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies
2. Configure environment variables
3. Set up database connection
4. Run the service

